# ---- 7. Very short, low-temperature stability test -------------------
# Only a brief, cold NVT nudge to confirm dynamics + QEq stay stable.
# Timestep 0.25 fs is conservative (methodology lists 0.25/0.5/1.0 fs as the
# values to test; Olou'ou Guifo et al. [4] used 0.5 and 0.1 fs).
velocity        all create 50.0 12345 mom yes rot yes dist gaussian
fix             nvt all nvt temp 50.0 50.0 25.0
timestep        0.25
run             100
